| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3091 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 78dd2b8b-b21a-5ed1-a1bb-eeb0f9a1625e"
